C ya monday, Logo!

::Zardus/Chordate::

Zardus laughs as he recieves Arcangel's transmission. Maximals like that 
amused him. He chuckles as he remembers Liono Prime acting a similar way. The 
Maximal commander had been a fairly good bot, but as a leader...

Zardus nods as he recieves Battera's transmission, turning to fire at Astral 
again.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Chordate frowns, recieving Rex's message. The Maximal checks the scanners to 
see a few other Maximals walking from the brig and into the CR chambers.

"Hey," he says, sending a transmission to them, "Rex might need some help in 
the brig CR chambers. When you're repaired, can you go to him? The door is 
locked to the brig CR room, so don't bust in."
